      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "HE'S A FELON (3) has recorded back to back wins, last time scoring at this track over 375m by 2.5 lengths (22.69). Yet to miss the placings from three starts out of this box. Great chance to get the job done again. ARCHER TWELVE (1) is a capable type and proved too strong last time to win by 0.8 lengths at this track in a handy 22.55 beating In The West. Goes well out of this box with a win and two minor placings. Can measure up again. HE'S A RIDDLER (2) filled a minor placing last start at this track behind HE'S A FELON (23.06) in a Grade 5. Has performed well from this box with a win and five minor placings to his name from nine starts. Bold showing expected. FAIRY KING PRAWN (8) is a last-start placegetter who is in the mix again.",
